@Comment:	Time is 0:24
@Comment:	older Sis (who may be a cousin) and Mot help Chi along by mouthing words to him. Chi reads very few words on his own , but context notes say he smiles and seems comfortable with this arrangement. Still , Chi seems to exclaim <oh no> each time he turns the page and finds more text to read. He identifies nouns from the pictures (when they aren't whispered to him) , and gets stuck on function words.
